where can i find the newsbreak ad network access token?

To fetch your API Access Token, please log in to the Newsbreak Admanager Platform. Click on Tools, then Resources, and select API Access Tokens. Here you can click 'Generate token' to create your own API access token. Remember that this token is tied to your user ID and should not be shared with anyone else.
